===Noun===
'''recrystallization'''
#{{chemistry}} a [[technique]] for the [[purification]] of [[chemical]] [[compound]]s in which the compound is [[dissolved]] in a [[solvent]] and slowly [[cooled]] to form [[crystal]]s
#{{geology}} a process in the formation of [[metamorphic]] [[rock]]s
#(''metallurgy'') the [[growth]] of [[grain]] [[fragment]]s in an [[alloy]], especially when it is [[worked]] by [[cold rolling]]
